{"tid":659430,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"大家會唔會因為自己女神既死而唔開心","createTime":"2018-05-09T20:37:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T23:13:05.000Z","uid":156666,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b8e2d28dd8a7d43bde8ec4d4deea868365b7a2a2","tid":659430,"uid":156666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T20:37:07.000Z","msg":"6年前我透過FB知道左一個女仔既存在<br />\n一開始都係當佢係普通女仔咁得閒睇下佢啲野咁<br />\n但不知不覺間就由得閒睇下變左做成日去睇佢FB,IG等<br />\n而佢亦不知不覺地成為左個既女神<br />\n呢6年我都有KEEP著睇佢既野<br />\n就算係DSE個陣都會睇下佢UPLODE既相同埋佢發既廢文<br />\n<br />\n但前幾日佢竟然因為意外過左身<br />\n由我得知件事到而家<br />\n每晚都訓唔著<br />\n一諗到以後既人生都冇得再見到佢UP既新相<br />\n以後都冇得再睇佢發新既廢文<br />\n以後佢既IG,FB都唔會再更新<br />\n從始就只能靠佢以前啲相同埋佢啲廢文黎回憶起佢<br />\n就覺得好唔開心<br />\n<br />\n雖然佢係間接陪左我六年既時間<br />\n但點講都係一個一面都未親眼見過既陌生人<br />\n佢就連我呢個人既存在都唔知道<br />\n但我就為佢既死而咁唔開心<br />\n<br />\n到底我正唔正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人可以話比我知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a28713559a72905d1183867ea969420a440b0d7c","tid":659430,"uid":156666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T20:49:27.000Z","msg":"冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd681300f77e793715c6532aae6180dc77e98bad","tid":659430,"uid":14065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T20:51:39.000Z","msg":"正常<br />\n<br />\n完"},{"pid":"02eb169efc5540efa834eca04341c9737a5a664a","tid":659430,"uid":156666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T20:59:48.000Z","msg":"冇左你叫我以後既人生點過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n女神我好唔捨得你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a89ddaae0b20f6d53113843ec37f1552e1e0504c","tid":659430,"uid":102187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-