T FD同佢一齊佢會更開心<br />\n<br />\n唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個男仔呢幾日一定喊到仆街<br />\n真係唔敢想像佢有幾唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b3a4fd72e9659b65a8923a15ffddbeb9887169e","tid":659430,"uid":156955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T21:46:59.000Z","msg":"近排都有個朋友走左<br />\n雖然唔係好熟<br />\n但成日都會諗起佢<br />\n不斷諗 以後呢個人只會出現係腦海<br />\n永遠都唔會再聽到佢把聲 見到佢個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就好sad 好sad<br />\n人真係好脆弱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f2c219f72ae40d7f11cc8d069891fee7477d51b","tid":659430,"uid":156666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T23:13:05.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"}]}